贝兹挑逗“大规模”和“有远见”的新专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/bez-teases-massive-and-visionary-new-album-from-happy-mondays-3838682?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bez-teases-massive-and-有远见的新Album-from-from-happy-MondaysDamian Jones Mon, 17 Feb 2025 16:17:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3838682 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="贝兹和肖恩·莱德" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我想听听你听过的最神奇的狗屎。我敢肯定我们可以交付它”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bez-teases-massive-and-visionary-new-album-from-happy-mondays-3838682">Bez的帖子嘲笑了《周一快乐》中的“大规模”和“有远见”的新专辑，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="贝兹和肖恩·莱德" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_bez_shaunryder_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bez">贝兹（Bez）</a>嘲笑了新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">《快乐星期一》</a>专辑的计划，这是自2007年“叔叔Dysfunktional”以来的第一张专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/happy-mondays-interview-mtv-emas-manchester-shaun-ryder-bez-biopic-new-album-tour-3812024">关于肖恩·莱德（Shaun Ryder）传记片的命运的周一快乐，并于2025年获得“重新恢复”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>去年11月， <em>NME</em>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SHAUN-RYDER">Shaun Ryder</a>进行了交谈， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/happy-mondays-interview-mtv-emas-manchester-shaun-ryder-bez-biopic-new-album-tour-3812024">他的Maraca摇晃起来，谈到了乐队在2025年与音乐“重新恢复”的计划</a>。</p><p>当时当时被问到2024年星期一的情况时，莱德回答：“安静，因为我们在2024年将其敲打在头上。我们出去做<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">黑葡萄</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">宇宙的咒语</a>，所以2025年我们会回来在它上。”</p><p>贝兹补充说：“我们再次将乐队重新聚在一起……再次！”</p><p>现在，贝兹说，乐队在被他们的经理<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alan-mcgee">艾伦·麦吉（Alan McGee）</a>说服回到录音室后正在制作新专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DCUivlnTb-N/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-g