m/artists/slash">Slash</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a>也在原始账单上，但现在他们将参加完整的乐队阵容。</p><p>除了现场演奏外，对机器成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">汤姆·莫雷洛（Tom Morello）的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">愤怒</a>还将担任该节目的音乐总监。它将由MOMOA托管和编写。</p><p> <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">标志性的重金属乐队将于7月5日星期六在伯明翰的家乡的Villa Park举行最后一场音乐会。</a>即将举行的演出将看到该乐队最具标志性的阵容 - 由主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a> ，吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-iommi">Tony Iommi</a> ，Bassist <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geezer-butler">Geezer Butler</a>和鼓手比尔·沃德（Bill Ward） - 二十年来第一次一起演奏。 </p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NZAoFoVv_uVCC6-TM2E5pz7ZInWq4mX1rtzrMTrf6HIRStQkqlB9eoyeE4Xi2HQdJfXWV6MYLBPfhuW_ZuirjqekxWUL3xn-TFzMjUkhz8zssXKwy2WlKCyap5JSroWOL4tkUjaHVvmSkIAjPO5U8RMvmB1vBheCXI=s0-d-e1-ft#https://mcusercontent.com/8de013f77985fee248af02718/images/095663b8-2a58-7cfe-a8cd-056e12e27f79.jpg" alt="https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NZAoFoVv_uVCC6-TM2E5pz7ZInWq4mX1rtzrMTrf6HIRStQkqlB9eoyeE4Xi2HQdJfXWV6MYLBPfhuW_ZuirjqekxWUL3xn-TFzMjUkhz8zssXKwy2WlKCyap5JSroWOL4tkUjaHVvmSkIAjPO5U8RMvmB1vBheCXI=s0-d-e1-ft#https://mcusercontent.com/8de013f77985fee248af02718/images/095663b8-2a58-7cfe-a8cd-056e12e27f79.jpg" /></p><p>安息日最终表演的所有利润将捐给慈善机构Cure Parkinson&#39;s，Birmingham儿童医院和Acorn Children&#39;s Hospice，这是由阿斯顿维拉（Aston Villa）支持的儿童临终关怀医院。</p><p>莎朗·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-interview-sharon-ozzy-osbourne-tony-iommi-health-birmingham-villa-park-final-show-new-material-3835523">最近在维拉公园（Villa Park）与Iommi一起在<em>NME</em>上发表讲话时</a>解释说，她的丈夫Ozzy目前在做“非常棒”，并对有史以来最后的安息日日期感到“非常激动”。她说：“这就是他想要的。”</p><p> “他想对所有人表示感谢。由于病的病，他没有机会，但是现在他确实有机会。”</p><p>沙龙告诉<em>NME</em> ，“回到起点”将是“庆祝仍然存在的旧音乐”，而不是黑色安息日事先发布任何新材料。</p><p>她解释说：“您进入职业生涯的舞台，无论您做什么都不能忍受您以前所做的事情。” “能够在桂冠上休息，说：&#39;人们仍然喜欢它，它仍然在卖出，我们不能比我们所做的事情更好”，这足够了。”</p><p>沙龙还将一次性日期描述为“庆祝活动 - 启动并将其传递给所有这些乐队的流派和先驱者”。她说：“通常，当您死了时，这事情就完成了 - 因此，这些家伙能够被感激！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551